{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_11_01_short",
  "title": "白石沙季 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、はい……なるほど……\nぜひ引き受けさせて下さい",
      "startTime": 5.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　千紗ですか？\n確かその日は……はい。私の方で確認してみますね",
      "startTime": 11.0317229703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "また後ほどご連絡させていただきます\nはい……では、お疲れ様です",
      "startTime": 22.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4100.000000000002,
          "startTime": 26.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、お姉ちゃん帰ってたんだ。おかえりなさい\n今日はお姉ちゃんが、お夕飯の当番だっけ？",
      "startTime": 31,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。これから作るところよ\nそれより千紗。少し話があるんだけど、いいかしら",
      "startTime": 38.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "今、{user}さんから連絡があってね\n今度、星見市で開催される春祭りについてなんだけど",
      "startTime": 46.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "そこでやるミニライブに\n良ければ出てみないかってお話をいただいたの",
      "startTime": 53.4000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……！　春祭りのライブにお姉ちゃんが出るの？\n昔、よく観に行ったよね。私、絶対に応援に行くね",
      "startTime": 61.7000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、私だけじゃないわよ。ちょうど予定も合うし\n千紗も一緒にどうかって話になっているの",
      "startTime": 72.3697997742,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}